  "body": "<!-- Please only use this template for submitting enhancement requests -->\r\n\r\n**What would you like to be added**:\r\n1) add metrics into kubelet to monitor [kubelet http server](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/e330c0120eed4871d518522b3f5c049c36a92464/pkg/kubelet/server/server.go#L83);\r\n2) add throttling to [kubelet http server](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/e330c0120eed4871d518522b3f5c049c36a92464/pkg/kubelet/server/server.go#L83). \r\n\r\n**Why is this needed**:\r\nKubelet provides lots of its functionalities through its http server, and currently there is no server-side monitoring and throttling mechanisms. \r\nAdding metrics into kubelet to monitor its http server will improve its observability and debuggability; adding throttling will prevent kubelet being overloaded from serving too many http requests.\r\n",
